00:18:45.520 --> 00:18:49.859
business decisions that may impact some of the much bigger budgets there.

00:18:49.859 --> 00:18:53.939
So I would say for different organizations, you would probably have different ways of

00:18:53.939 --> 00:18:58.500
evaluating that, but let's not just limit to the amount of users or the amount of requests

00:18:58.500 --> 00:18:59.500
that it handles.

00:18:59.500 --> 00:19:00.500
Okay.

